About Woodall’s Village
55+ Active Mobile Home & RV Community in Lakeland, Fl!
Situated in beautiful Lakeland, Florida, Woodall’s Mobile Home Village is an attractive age-restricted RV/Mobile home community with over 200 lots and a variety of activities to compliment all lifestyles.
Surrounded by beautiful lakes, wildlife preserves, beaches and theme parks, residents and vacationers alike have the choice of many area attractions to explore. Our central location allows residents to be close to big cities while still being able to enjoy the peace and quiet of the suburbs.
Or stay at home and enjoy our community activities and lifestyle, which includes a sparkling in ground heated pool, a spacious activities clubhouse, a library, shuffleboard, and so much more.
Community News
Stay up-to-date on everything going on in our community!
Woodall’s Mobile Home Village’s Private Community News section is a place where news, community meeting minutes, hurricane preparedness, and other important information can be made available for our residents. Here, residents can login to access this important information.
If you are a resident that has lost or forgotten your login information, please consult the
Woodall’s Mobile Home Village’s Office
for login information retrieval.
